England, United Kingdom":"Ewelme, Oxfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Ewelme, Oxfordshire, England":"Ewelme, Oxfordshire, Angleterre","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Sir John de Burghersh, Knt est né le 29 septembre 1343, à Ewelme, Oxfordshire, Angleterre, son père, John de Burghersh, avait 19 ans et sa mère, Maud de Kerdeston, avait 26 ans. Il a épousé Ismania Lady Baroness Kerdeston deHanham en 1372, à Gloucestershire, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 2 filles. Sa profession de son indiquée est sheriff à Somerset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il est décédé le 21 septembre 1391, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 47 ans, et a été enterré à Ewelme, Oxfordshire, Angleterre."},"de":{"29 September 1343–21 September 1391":"29. September 1343–21. September 1391","1343–1391":"1343–1391","1335–1420":"1335–1420","1379–1437":"1379–1437","–1421":"–1421","1324–1349":"1324–1349","1318–1349":"1318–1349","30 June 1349":"30. Juni 1349","30 September 1343":"30. September 1343","1372":"1372","21 September 1391":"21. September 1391","1382":"1382","20 May 1349":"20. Mai 1349","1391":"1391","1349":"1349","1437":"1437","1379":"1379","1324":"1324","1335":"1335","1421":"1421","1420":"1420","1343":"1343","29 September 1343":"29. September 1343","about 1343":"um 1343","1318":"1318","Ewelme, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Ewelme, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom","Ewelme, Oxfordshire, England":"Ewelme, Oxfordshire, England","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, England","lifeSummary":"Als Sir John de Burghersh, Knt am 29. September 1343 in Ewelme, Oxfordshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater John de Burghersh 19 und seine Mutter Maud de Kerdeston 26. Er hat 1372 in Gloucestershire, England Ismania Lady Baroness Kerdeston deHanham geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Töchter. sein Beruf ist als sheriff in Somerset, England, United Kingdom aufgeführt. Er starb am 21. September 1391 im Alter von 47 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort u